				<td colspan="2"><span>That's Scarlet Desert btw... and yes this is a very fun, yet dangerous, place to play.  I have hardly soloed, for xp, with my bard but this place was really fun to go to with my druid and a pally friend.  The revnants and the such are undead, remember you're on the light side of Luclin which means most everything is evil and will hate you, yet you will get many rewards for killing things in the Scarlet Desert.
<br />

<br />
Things to remember while hunting in SD:
<br />

<br />
1. Anything that has a name will drop something of use.
<br />

<br />
2. Antyhing of worth is lore so don't bother trying to farm multiple items.
<br />

<br />
3. Just about everything there will hate you.
<br />

<br />
4. The only things there that can see invis are the Revnants.</span></td>
